= Buildslave on Windows =

* Get the latest Python 2.7 and install it in `c:\Python27`
* Get the C++ compiler for Python 2.7 from MS
* Install latest Git for Windows with pull and commit as-it-is
* Latest python will come with pip, so using pip install `buildbot-slave virtualenv wheel`
* Install the build-slave workdir in `c:\buildslave`